{"tid":2445660,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"｛數學題｝AIA保障無限種疾病有冇違反商品說明條例？","createTime":"2021-03-13T20:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T02:42:25.000Z","uid":29132,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"68fcac8191052afd105cbfe4d19bdd2cff755200","tid":2445660,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T20:23:15.000Z","msg":"近排睇電視成日睇到AIA個廣告，睇睇吓我就喺到諗：AIA宣稱保障任何一種疾病，只要符合佢個4乘3框架就得啦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZEpPdz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZEpPdz.png&h=14a9b2bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GK1RyS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GK1RyS.png&h=c8fab066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為佢係放諸將來所有可能性同未知性，固然係被延展成無盡架啦，所以佢宣稱保障無限種疾病。<br />\n<br />\n咁問題就嚟啦，疾病固然因未知性而係無限，但框架以外不被保障嘅疾病，都會因為將來嘅無限延展而變成無限<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以就出現咗兩個無限，疾病嘅無限同不受保疾病嘅無限。<br />\n<br />\n咁無限減無限，咁仲係唔係無限？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或者有人會講，任何一種疾病一定多過唔受保嘅疾病，咁有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有疾病大於不受保疾病，就咁推論係啱嘅，但當放入無限嘅概念就唔係咁講，因為喺大多數數學概念中，無論係幾份之幾嘅無限，都係無限<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以去翻標題到，咁AIA提供嘅係無限減無限種疾病嘅保障，咁係唔係無限？<br />\n<br />\n大多數概念中，無限減無限係未被定義（undefined），咁問題就嚟，究竟AIA宣傳無限有冇違反商品說明條例？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭盔：學術討論，不是指控<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e31e82444eb7d03e7f6a7c97873613ac0f1d8b2","tid":2445660,"uid":51006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T20:30:23.000Z","msg":"單數無限<br />\n雙數無限<br />\n正整數無限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nset theory <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e72115f283a97a4b25b4d59df8d50ee14a07324","tid":2445660,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T20:31:50.000Z","msg":"無限有分大小<br />\n最細既係可數既無限<br />\n受保同唔受保疾病都係可數無限，所以兩個無限係一樣<br />\n利伸：好似係"},{"pid":"61cbe8ec1bd65145c7c5f79b31cd93e2960f467e","tid":2445660,"uid":117893,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T20:34:58.000Z","msg":"叫佢拎走「不保事項」先好講人無限啦"},{"pid":"41a808c58c6602c0a7cd219bfaa2cf4dbc63916c","tid":2445660,"uid":275030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T20:35:43.000Z","msg":"賠1蚊都係賠，又無話保證賠幾多比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb8c8d3b476f8c700668e68e8126c059a5dc5a6","tid":2445660,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:38:16.000Z","msg":"我一直都好期待會唔會有數學家入嚟解釋我個無限理論啱唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果錯咗冇人話我知 好柒架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7f0c37cab155d05838a78895952d43af9f4ccd","tid":2445660,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:42:25.000Z","msg":"如果我用呢個理論去報海關，海關會唔會受理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}